data.description: Come see this adorable 2-bedroom house located Faith Village. The home has recently been renovated with new luxury vinyl flooring, fresh paint, and a completely updated bathroom. Original hardwood floors remain in some parts of the home and has energy efficient windows throughout. The bathrooms new features include new shower-tub combo, flooring, vanity, and faucets. There are three separate living-den areas, where the third could be easily transitioned into a third bedroom if doors are added. Kitchen is open which makes for easy entertainment and has tons of built in storage. Both bedrooms are good size, and both have their own closet. The backyard has HUGE covered Patio, privacy fence, fire pit, and big natural trees that makes it enjoyable in any season. Two car garage located in back of house with access through ally. The home is in an established neighborhood close to shopping, restaurants, parks, and amazing schools!You won't want to miss this opportunity to make this home yours!
